		(property "Description" "Power-OR diode: USB VBUS into V5_OR node, allows USB-only bench powering/flashing. Pin 2 (A/anode) faces J2's VBUS; pin 1 (K/cathode) faces the V5_OR node. Ultra-low-VF Schottky swap for 1N5819W (2026-07-16): 255mV typ @100mA. Order PMEG3015EH,115 - LCSC C552867."
