		(property "Description" "12V rail bulk cap for WS2815 LED load steps; place at power IN connector. SMD V-chip aluminum electrolytic (2026-07-16, was TH radial): RVT1E471M1010, 10x10.2mm, LCSC C72518. NOT tantalum - low-impedance 12V bus + hot-plug inrush is the classic tantalum surge-failure scenario."
